# Student Exam Score Prediction using Linear Regression

## Problem Statement
To predict student final exam score based on study hours, attendance and previous score.

## Dataset Description
The dataset contains 20 rows with features:
- Study Hours
- Attendance
- Previous Score
- Final Score (Target)

## Model Used
Linear Regression from Scikit-Learn.

## Results
Model achieved good R2 score indicating strong linear relationship.
Feature engineering improved performance.

## Conclusion
Study hours and previous performance significantly affect final exam score.
Model generalizes well with train-test split.
